How to handle a Session

Javascript does not handle
sesssion storage.

/App.jsx

Create a logic if it is user connected

ifUserLoggedIn.mjs

function isUserLoggedIn {
    return !!sessionStorage.username
}

export default ifUserLoggedIn

import logic to App.jsx
this.state { logic.ifUserLoggedIn ? home : view}
add ifUserLoggedIn in logic/index

change all files .mjs to .js

if there's index.mjs you change
replace space instead.

you can delete all formats .jsx, js ad msj. 
But you cannot delete .css extension

